<template lang="pug">
	.selection-one
		block-header(color = 'white')
		poster
		description
		block-footer
</template>

<script>
	import Header from '../blocks/includes/header.vue';
	import Footer from '../blocks/includes/footer.vue';

	import Poster from '../blocks/one-winner/poster.vue';
	import Description from '../blocks/one-winner/description.vue';
	import AOS from 'aos';
		
	export default {
		name: 'One-winner',
		data: function(){
			return {}
		},
		components:{
			'block-header': Header,
			'block-footer': Footer,
			'poster': Poster,
			'description': Description,
		},
		mounted() {
			this.$nextTick(function() {
				AOS.init({
					once: true,
					disabled: 'mobile',
					// offset: 0,
					duration: 1000
				});
			});
		}
	}
</script>

<style lang="scss">
	@import '@/assets/sass/ui.scss';
	@import '@/helpers/sass/aos.scss';
</style>
